item.title: Compile Errors
item.dc:creator: @bumbumlongtime bumbumlongtime
item.description:
@bumbumlongtime wrote:

On a compile error, it actuly tells you what file it is in and what line it is on, take the first error for instance

client.java:4: 'class' or 'interface' expected import java.util.GregorianCalendar; ^

at the start it say’s

client.java:4:

in other words its in client.jav on line 4
